										<h3 class="widget-title"><span class="wow bounce" style="visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;">MISSION BBD</span></h3>
                                       <div class="service col-md-offset-2 col-md-8 col-xs-12">

                                          <div class="text-font-family service-desc wow fadeInUp animated" style="visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;">
                                             <p class="dropcap"> Outside the central hall on the first floor, where most of the action is taking place, there are âwar roomsâ named after some of the biggest sports icons: Tendulkar, Federer and so on. The biggest of these rooms is called âThe Olympics.â It is right across a flight of stairs leading to the floor. </p>
<p>The Olympics is the command centre for the Big Billion Days (BBD) sale. Inside, a crack team of Flipkart leaders including Kalyan Krishnamurthy, Samardeep Subandh, and Saikiran Krishnamurthy is on to analytics of the sale. CEO Bansal walks into the room and settles down in front of a giant screen which throws up numbers and charts. </p>


