	                                       <div class="service col-md-offset-2 col-md-8 col-xs-12">
	                                          <div class="text-font-family service-desc wow fadeInUp animated" style="visibility: visible; ">
	                                            <p class="dropcap"> Two hours after the sale kicks off we meet CEO Binny Bansal in a small conference room. Wearing a green hoodie and a pair of jeans, he sits cross legged looking overwhelmed. When Binny and Sachin started Flipkart in September 2007, they were a tiny startup running out of an apartment and didnât think they would come this far. The nine years have been stupendous.</p><p>

âThe next nine years are going to be completely different,â says Binny.</p><p>

Even raising additional funding for instance, will not be a purely financial decision. âWe will look for strategic partners,â he says.</p>


